<tal:block tal:define="
opt python:options or path('context/@@unitraccsearch/getLocalsearch_kwargs');
brains opt/brains;
list_macro nocall:opt/func/list_macro;
SearchableText request/form/SearchableText | nothing;
bsize python:int(request.form.get('b_size', 25));
batch python:here.getBrowser('batch')(brains, int(bsize));
"
i18n:domain="plone"><tal:comment replace="nothing"><!--
Aufgerufen durch
 ../../../skins/unitracc_templates/localsearch_view.pt
Erstellt aus Kopie von 
 ../../../skins/unitracc_templates/kss-search-result.pt


